--- Requisites
Xilinx Virtex-5 FPGA ML507
PowerPC 440 synthesis
MÃ¤rklin Digital controler synthesis
Embedded Linux BootLoader

It is required to build a bootloader with consists on a compressed image of the synthesis files along with and Embedded Linux Kernel executable file compiled for PPC440 architecture. This composition must be stored into a compact flash card with two partitions, the first partition contains the bootloader itself, the second one contains a non-volative embedded linux root file system.
 
--- Instalation Notes
Please, place maerkserv folder under /home/root/ in the server machine (Virtex 5 FPGA, PowerPC 440 synthetized, Embedded Linux with rootfs).
Please, place maerkcli folder wherever you want in the client machine.